ItemObject, PlayerObject
public abstract class DynamicGameObject
extends GameObject

DynamicGameObject extends GameObject. DynamicGameObject Loads information on dynamic objects within the game level and runs the predefined scripts which dictate the actions and behaviors of each object.

Version:
DynamicGameObject.java,v 0.1 2006/10/03
Author:

Method Detail

destroy

public void destroy()
This method calls the protected onDestroy method, which cannot be invoked outside the DynamicGameObject class. This allows the application to do a little bit of cleaning up and double checking before actually calling the scripts that run upon its removal.
